name: Elizabeth Bioshock Lora
description:
I couldn't find an Elizabeth Lora anywhere, so I made my own! Let me know what you think?

For my examples I use the following:

Classic Elizabeth: <lora:Elizabeth:0.6>, Elizabeth, regoutfit, woman, blue jacket, blue skirt, ((pure white corset)), chocker, blue eyes, short black hair

Burial at Sea Elizabeth: <lora:Elizabeth:0.6>, Elizabeth, dlcoutfit, woman, white shirt, ((white collared shirt)), (Black skirt:1.2), ((pencil skirt)), red belt, (red necklace), shoulder length black hair, blue eyes

I think it comes out pretty well, I haven't really tried it without the default clothing, or with too much NSFW content.

If you've got more idea, please let me know!

Want me to make a LORA for you: https://www.fiverr.com/s2/c47476ec9d

If you want to support me, find my patreon and Fanbox at: https://www.patreon.com/LMJA18 and https://lmja18.fanbox.cc/ or see more of my images over at https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/52924269
